  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Tuas)",
  "description": "<h4><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Receive and inspect incoming goods for accuracy and damage.</li>\n  <li>Unload, unpack, and label items for storage.</li>\n  <li>Match goods with delivery orders, invoices, or purchase orders.</li>\n  <li>Store items in designated areas according to standard procedures (e.g., FIFO/FEFO).</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper handling of items.</li>\n  <li>Assist in cycle counts and stock-taking exercises.</li>\n  <li>Report any discrepancies or stock damages to supervisors.</li>\n  <li>Pick and pack items accurately for delivery or customer orders.</li>\n  <li>Prepare items for dispatch including labeling, scanning, and documentation.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the warehouse area.</li>\n  <li>Ensure aisles and exits are free of obstructions.</li>\n  <li>Follow safety protocols.</li>\n  <li>Operate basic warehouse equipment (e.g., pallet jack, trolley).</li>\n  <li>Perform basic upkeep of equipment and report issues promptly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
